<p><strong>How to cancel an appointment </strong></p>
<p>Your appointment letter should have a telephone number listed for changing or cancelling your appointment.</p>
<p>You can also telephone the Appointments Call Centre on <strong>01562 512312</strong> if you need assistance with changing an appointment.</p></div>
